name: OutdoorSoundsforSleep
0:

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: outdoor sounds
des: What better sounds to sleep to than the sounds of the great outdoors! Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Outdoor Sounds,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
